distance(lat1,lon1,lat2,lon2,unit){var radlat1=Math.PI*lat1/180;var radlat2=Math.PI*lat2/180;var radlon1=Math.PI*lon1/180;var radlon2=Math.PI*lon2/180;var theta=lon1-lon2;var radtheta=Math.PI*theta/180;var dist=Math.sin(radlat1)*Math.sin(radlat2)+Math.cos(radlat1)*Math.cos(radlat2)*Math.cos(radtheta);dist=Math.acos(dist);dist=dist*180/Math.PI;dist=dist*60*1.1515;if(unit==\"K\"){dist=dist*1.609344;}\nif(unit==\"N\"){dist=dist*0.8684;}\nreturn dist;krpano().set(\"dist\",dist);}\nfunction ucfirst(str){str+='';var f=str.charAt(0).toUpperCase();return f+str.substr(1).toLowerCase();};function slugify(text)\n{return text.toString().toLowerCase().replace(/\\s+/g,'-').replace(new RegExp(\"\\\\s\",'g'),\"\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"a\").replace(new RegExp(\"\",'g'),\"ae\").replace(new RegExp(\"\",'g'),\"c\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"e\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"i\").replace(new RegExp(\"\",'g'),\"n\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"o\").replace(new RegExp(\"\",'g'),\"oe\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"u\").replace(new RegExp(\"[]\",'g'),\"y\").replace(new RegExp(\"\\\\W\",'g'),\"\").replace(/[^\\w\\-]+/g,'').replace(/\\-\\-+/g,'-').replace(/^-+/,'').replace(/-+$/,'');};};;var mapresultFallback=new function(){var self=this;var cache={};var
